{"tid":2494728,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九巴獨設回水機制！！！！！","createTime":"2021-04-18T17:59:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T19:32:22.000Z","uid":146917,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5e7593066ca7a730bff9e955ae359ec405991c99","tid":2494728,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T17:59:31.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】搭巴士遇上八達通不夠錢，又無零錢付車資，有市民可能會無奈地取出鈔票多付車費，雖然現時九巴、新巴、城巴及大嶼山巴士等四家專利巴士公司，都不設車資找續服務，但原來這類「豪畀你睇」九巴乘客，事後或有可能獲巴士公司「回水」。<br />\n九巴員工協會理事長李國華表示，多付車資的市民可即時告知車長，車長會登記乘客個人資料及寫報告給公司確認事件，九巴接獲當事人求助及確認事件後，會於一個月內將多付款額交回。另有九巴資深車長稱，其實公司有內部指引，若果乘客帶不夠錢，司機可讓乘客登車，但要提醒乘客下次補付車資。不過，另三家巴士公司就「多謝晒!」，因為他們並無相關退款機制，所以巴士公司提醒乘客，切記「帶定散子搭巴士」。"},{"pid":"818a5949da89f44a71e9d161303443120e745a90","tid":2494728,"uid":29514,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T18:02:08.000Z","msg":"你試下叫個司機幫你抄資料囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌返你轉頭再問你係咪發緊夢"},{"pid":"07c09dd66483b64e1041c10ed6f2fc4435ce08d4","tid":2494728,"uid":191453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T18:05:43.000Z","msg":"愚人節?"},{"pid":"148a7869dff592de306968397864a7cc707b8b22","tid":2494728,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T18:11:56.000Z","msg":"冇source當你老作<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf8b694448cd0a869d747db32cce24957b3d2e2e","tid":2494728,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T18:25:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20150113/LLK5VW5EH4GQK5B47OZYC6HM3I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20150113%2FLLK5VW5EH4GQK5B47OZYC6HM3I%2F&d=ZGEEaRoo4ZESsTiVlrSVponMh2OwnA7FCi%2BsKpr4SDY%3D&h=9919ce8f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20150113%2FLLK5VW5EH4GQK5B47OZYC6HM3I%2F&h=a9af3745\" data-auto-link 